1
00:00:14,223 --> 00:00:17,570
- I said, no.
- A sapphire waterfall!

2
00:00:17,670 --> 00:00:19,554
It's a waterfall, made of sapphires!

3
00:00:19,829 --> 00:00:21,460
<i>This enormous jewel,
size of a glacier,</i>

4
00:00:21,560 --> 00:00:24,640
reaches the Cliffs of Oblivion, then
shatters into sapphires at the edge,

5
00:00:24,740 --> 00:00:27,561
they fall 100,000 feet
into a crystal ravine.

6
00:00:27,661 --> 00:00:31,735
- I bet you say that to all the girls.
- Oh, come on, they're boarding now.

7
00:00:31,835 --> 00:00:34,230
It's no fun on my own.
Four hours, that's all it takes.

8
00:00:34,637 --> 00:00:38,869
<i>No, that's four hours there and four
hours back, that's like a school trip.</i>

9
00:00:38,969 --> 00:00:41,096
- I'd rather go sunbathing!
- You be careful.

10
00:00:41,440 --> 00:00:42,996
<i>That's X-tonic sunlight.</i>

11
00:00:43,096 --> 00:00:47,455
Oh, I'm safe. It says in the brochure,
this glass is 15-feet thick.

12
00:00:47,555 --> 00:00:48,660
<i>All right, I give up.</i>

13
00:00:48,760 --> 00:00:51,484
Back for dinner, we'll try that
antigravity restaurant. With bibs.

14
00:00:51,584 --> 00:00:52,335
<i>That's a date.</i>

15
00:00:52,621 --> 00:00:53,747
Well, not a date.

16
00:00:53,847 --> 00:00:55,719
Oh, you know what I mean.
Oh, get off!

17
00:00:55,957 --> 00:00:57,100
- See you later.
- Oy!

18
00:00:57,200 --> 00:00:59,569
- And you be careful, all right?
- Naaah.

19
00:00:59,669 --> 00:01:00,670
Taking a big space truck

20
00:01:00,770 --> 00:01:03,326
with bunch of strangers across
diamond planet called Midnight?

21
00:01:03,426 --> 00:01:04,965
What could possibly go wrong?

22
